lethal.descriptionLabel: Retrievable knife that is lethal on impact. Note: This equipment can be obtained from the Dr. Karlov Lives Bundle when available in the store and has no functional difference from the ^5Throwing Knife^7, change is visual only.

lethal.name: equip_throwing_knife_fire
lethal.label: Flaming Throwing Knife
lethal.descriptionLabel: Retrievable knife that is lethal on impact. Note: This equipment can be obtained from the Pyromaniac Bundle when available in the store and has no functional difference from the ^5Throwing Knife^7, change is visual only.

tactical.name: equip_adrenaline
tactical.label: Stim
tactical.descriptionLabel: Military stimulant that cauterizes combat wounds and refreshes Tactical Sprint.

tactical.name: equip_decoy
tactical.label: Decoy Grenade
tactical.descriptionLabel: Counter-intel grenade that simulates fake gunfire and radar signatures that confuse the enemy.

tactical.name: equip_gas_grenade
tactical.label: Gas Grenade
tactical.descriptionLabel: Explodes on impact with the ground, releasing a lingering cloud of tear gas that causes slowed movement, blurred vision, and coughing.

tactical.name: equip_hb_sensor
tactical.label: Heartbeat Sensor
tactical.descriptionLabel: A tablet that displays rough information about nearby enemies.

tactical.name: equip_smoke
tactical.label: Smoke Grenade
tactical.descriptionLabel: Deploys a smoke screen that blocks vision and automated targeting systems.

tactical.name: equip_snapshot_grenade
tactical.label: Snapshot Grenade
tactical.descriptionLabel: Provides a momentary glimpse of enemies within the blast radius.

precision_airstrike.name: precision_airstrike
precision_airstrike.label: Precision Airstrike
precision_airstrike.descriptionLabel: Call in twin jets for a precision strike along the best available path.

scrambler_drone_escort.name: scrambler_drone_escort
scrambler_drone_escort.label: Counter UAV
scrambler_drone_escort.descriptionLabel: A drone that scrambles all enemy minimaps, regardless of distance, and incrementally disrupts their HUD the closer they get to the targeted area.

airdrop.name: airdrop
airdrop.label: Care Package
airdrop.descriptionLabel: Call in a random killstreak care package to your location.

radar_drone_overwatch.name: radar_drone_overwatch
radar_drone_overwatch.label: Personal Radar
radar_drone_overwatch.descriptionLabel: Escort drone that reveals nearby enemies on the minimap and audibly pings them in the world.

uav.name: uav
uav.label: UAV
uav.descriptionLabel: UAV recon ship that reveals enemy locations on the minimap.

cruise_predator.name: cruise_predator
cruise_predator.label: Cruise Missile
cruise_predator.descriptionLabel: Control a long range cruise missile with boost capabilities.

airdrop_multiple.name: airdrop_multiple
airdrop_multiple.label: Emergency Airdrop
airdrop_multiple.descriptionLabel: Call in 3 random killstreak care packages to your location.

manual_turret.name: manual_turret
manual_turret.label: Shield Turret
manual_turret.descriptionLabel: A manual shielded turret that can be deployed on most surfaces.

white_phosphorus.name: white_phosphorus
white_phosphorus.label: White Phosphorus
white_phosphorus.descriptionLabel: Cover the battlefield with white smoke incendiary canisters that will weaken the enemy and burn any that wander too close.

hover_jet.name: hover_jet
hover_jet.label: VTOL Jet
hover_jet.descriptionLabel: Releases an initial missile barrage before guarding a location of the player's choice.

directional_uav.name: directional_uav
directional_uav.label: Advanced UAV
directional_uav.descriptionLabel: An untargetable orbital UAV that reveals the enemy's direction on the minimap in real time.

chopper_gunner.name: chopper_gunner
chopper_gunner.label: Chopper Gunner
chopper_gunner.descriptionLabel: Control an assault chopper armed with a turret and air-to-land missiles.

gunship.name: gunship
gunship.label: Gunship
gunship.descriptionLabel: A heavy assault gunship with three types of armaments.

sentry_gun.name: sentry_gun
sentry_gun.label: Sentry Gun
sentry_gun.descriptionLabel: Automated turret that scans for nearby enemies.

toma_strike.name: toma_strike
toma_strike.label: Cluster Strike
toma_strike.descriptionLabel: Signal for a number of cluster mortars to hit the designated location.

juggernaut.name: juggernaut
juggernaut.label: Juggernaut
juggernaut.descriptionLabel: Call in a care package that contains the Juggernaut assault gear.  The minigun will drop when the Juggernaut dies.

pac_sentry.name: pac_sentry
pac_sentry.label: Wheelson
pac_sentry.descriptionLabel: Remote controlled UGV with a powerful airburst turret.

chopper_support.name: chopper_support
chopper_support.label: Support Helo
chopper_support.descriptionLabel: Call in a heavy assault helo with twin turrets to patrol the map.

scrambler_drone_guard.name: scrambler_drone_guard
scrambler_drone_guard.label: Counter UAV
scrambler_drone_guard.descriptionLabel: A drone that scrambles all enemy minimaps, regardless of distance, and incrementally disrupts their HUD the closer they get to the targeted area.

bradley.name: bradley
bradley.label: Infantry Assault Vehicle
bradley.descriptionLabel: A manned light infantry vehicle with a .50 cal machine gun on top.
